<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 A tum tikah, a tum tikah, A dawtmi khamh awkah, Amah lungvar, sungmi
 lungvar, Jesuh dawtmi hna.

[C1]
   Amah sumthawng an dawhter, Deirel arfi bangin, An i dawhnak in a
   ceu, A sumthawng lungvar.

[V2]
 A khawmh hna lai, a khawmh hna lai, A peng chung chiah awkah, A thiang
 a ceumi vialte kha, Jesuh dawtmi hna.

[C2]
   Amah sumthawng an dawhter, Deirel arfi bangin, An i dawhnak in a
   ceu, A sumthawng lungvar.

[V3]
 Ngakchia no hna, ngakchia sem hna, Jesuh a dawtmi hna, A thimmi
 lungvar sung an si, A ngaite an si.

[C3]
   Amah sumthawng an dawhter, Deirel arfi bangin, An i dawhnak in a
   ceu, A sumthawng lungvar.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
<title>LUNGVAR SUNG CH382</title>
<hymn_number>382</hymn_number>
</song>